OL,5, Businesses that use high levels of     
OL,6, energy are to get more support from the
OL,7, government for electricity costs.      
OL,9,FMinisters said an Energy Intensive     
OL,10,FIndustries Compensation Scheme will be 
OL,11,Fextended for a further three years and 
OL,12,Fits budget will be more than doubled.  
OL,14,FThe support comes as firms and         
OL,15,Fhouseholds are being hit by higher     
OL,16,Fenergy bills, driven by soaring global 
OL,17,Fwholesale gas prices.                  
OL,19,FUK Steel said the extension of the     
OL,20,Fsupport was "much needed".             
